@startuml

actor User as "ユーザー"

participant AuthController
participant AuthService
participant UserRepository
participant PasswordEncoder
participant JwtProvider

User -> AuthController : POST /api/auth/login\n(email, password)

AuthController -> AuthService : authenticate(email, password)

AuthService -> UserRepository : findByEmail(email)

alt ユーザーが存在する

    UserRepository --> AuthService : User

    AuthService -> PasswordEncoder : matches(password, user.getPassword())

    alt パスワード一致

        PasswordEncoder --> AuthService : true

        AuthService -> JwtProvider : generateToken(userId)

        JwtProvider --> AuthService : token

        AuthService --> AuthController : AuthResponseDto(token, role)

        AuthController --> User : 200 OK\ntoken, roleを返却

    else パスワード不一致

        PasswordEncoder --> AuthService : false

        AuthService --> AuthController : AuthException

        AuthController --> User : 401 Unauthorized

    end

else ユーザーが存在しない

    UserRepository --> AuthService : Optional.empty

    AuthService --> AuthController : AuthException

    AuthController --> User : 401 Unauthorized

end

@enduml